room_title: Escape room "The Gallery" by Escape Rhode Island in Providence
review: Did the gallery last night with nine other friends. We had a blast! The puzzles are challenging and require a lot of thought, communication, and teamwork. Great value and awesome staff. Would definitely do it again in the future!
